title.narrative: UK-China Collaboration on Forest Governance & Trade

description.narrative: This activity (UK-China Collaboration on Forest Governance & Trade) is a component of Forest Governance, Markets and Climate reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £594,306. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Forestry policy and administrative management. The start date is 01-04-2012 and the end date is 30-04-2023.
